  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So you can do something like:\n\n``` js\n// with an instantsearch instance:\nvar search = instantsearch(....);\nwindow.location.href = '.../' + search.createURL({facetsRefinements: {category: 'Home'}});\n\n// or by just calling the static method:\nwindow.location.href = '...#' + instantsearch.createQueryString({facetsRefinements: {category: 'Home'}});\n```\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-28T12:42:18Z",
